Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HtmlComponent
    Interface to be used by all components to be drawn using the TextWindow.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HtmlFragment
    A single element of HTML to be rendered by a TextWindow, containing text, font and color.
    HtmlPrinter
    A client that manages printing to a TextWindow.
    HtmlTag
    A HtmlComponent for HTML-style tags, such as the br and hr tags.
    SimpleBrowser
    The main class for SimpleBrowser, a program that can help pretty-print tokenized HTML.
    TextWindow
    Performs the actual rendering of HtmlComponents.
